title: Sauce Remix Discography 2010-2011 (2 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
SAUCE REMIX DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 2 releases...

 * 2010 - Bible On My Side
 * 2011 - Soul Food

Banging beats, amazing lyrics, mesmerizing hooks, positive messages that can change the world and a live performance that will inspire anyone from any age group or culture, this is all wrapped up in the Kansas City native rapper "Sauce Remix". A local artist with a national appeal, hopefully making it to that status and more, Sauce has been steam-rolling with positive art since 2008 and this train of hope doesn't seem to be slowing down.

For Him,
TorrentTracts - December 2013
